caption:
Corn is a key source of nutrition for much of the world. Ensuring efficient production of this staple crop, and furthering nutrition for Sub-Saharan Africa, is a key part of our commitment to our mission, Health for all, Hunger for none.

By tripling our capacity for high-quality seed, we aim to double the number of smallholder farmers we reach by 2030. Together, we can build a more sustainable future!
